{"tid":390968,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"20:45【變形金剛5：最後的騎士 2017】","createTime":"2017-09-07T12:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T12:42:19.000Z","uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4ea11a2537fb787ea161d8b1890e77d812e13a","tid":390968,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.simbla.com%2F871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a%2Fiusee&d=8IT2q3P%2Bda4EDq8PYwT7BFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=34a37cf0\" target=\"_blank\">http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee</a><br />\n<br />\n　　《變形金剛5：最後的騎士》打破了《變形金剛》系列的核心故事，重新定義了人們心目中的英雄形像。人類和變形金剛開戰，擎天柱失蹤，拯救未來的關鍵就埋藏在歷史的秘密之中，那是地球上變形金剛的歷史。拯救世界的責任落在一支非同尋常的隊伍身上：凱德&middot;伊格爾（馬克&middot;沃爾伯格飾）、大黃蜂、一位英國爵士（安東尼&middot;霍普金斯飾）還有一位牛津大學教授（勞拉&middot;哈德克飾）。 <br />\n　　每個人一生中都會遇到這樣一個時刻，它召喚著我們去改變世界。在《變形金剛5：最後的騎士》中，一直被追捕的人將成為英雄，英雄會變成反派。我們和他們的世界，只能存活一個。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hasbro.com/common/productimages/zh_Hant_HK/f162a44050569047f534682b1299cc53/50d83bd60de6df3ad511a0b1db3e0b7b10d97878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hasbro.com%2Fcommon%2Fproductimages%2Fzh_Hant_HK%2Ff162a44050569047f534682b1299cc53%2F50d83bd60de6df3ad511a0b1db3e0b7b10d97878.jpg&h=3088bbc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"709d09ff829b70fb2cc21370a4cd8c1ebb269a98","tid":390968,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6227098603df7617af83837b05cae39f8a961e97","tid":390968,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}